short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The easy way to get information's about your current Microsoft Teams Tenant!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The "Dev Helper for Teams" is designed to simplify the tasks of developing and supporting Microsoft Teams Apps. In the current version of Dev Helper for Teams, you can copy the tenant ID of the currently open Microsoft Teams Web App to your clipboard with one click. 

Try it out right now!
